value:
Rrrghh... My blood...courses through
my veins like rivers of fire...

When I was a child...a calming lullaby
was sung to me... Could that be what
has kept me sane?

Mist, Soren, Titania... Stay back...
That's...an order...

Father... One day, my strength will
rival even yours...

Battle... I must temper myself
in the heat of battle... Bring me
the strongest among you...

I must leave this place... If I stay here
any longer, I may...lose control...

I won't lose to anything. ANYTHING!
Least of all this rage inside me!

Where is my next opponent? Show
yourselfâ€”now!

More... Give me more...
The bloodshed has only
just begun...
This will...help me achieve my goal...

I am Ike. My blade...hungers. Point
me toward something to fight....
Something that will fight back...

You need not worry after me.$k$pI seek the power to protect those
closest to me. To protect...
my friends.$k$pIf this rage swirling inside me can
be forced into submission, then
I will be worthy of wielding it.$k$pBut that is my struggle... I must
tame this beast...make it my own.
I cannot let myself fear it...$k$pI will face it head on, and overcome
it... That is what it means to be
burdened with such power...
Ooooooh!
Die...!
Gah...
What...!?
Hraaaagh!
I'll...destroy it all!
Stay back.
Hate! Hate!
What...happened...
Uh...
I...am Ike. I lead the Greil Mercenaries...
Ugh! Don't touch me.
Wipe it all away. Everything...
Freedom... Chaos... Transformation... Future... Mystery...
If this continues... I will kill them all. I must... stop...
My father... Him, too... On that day... That day... He...
If I lose control... Stop me. I'm...I'm counting on you.
Yes...
What...now?
You...choose.
